# =============================================================================
# KOS (Knowledge Organization System) Concepts and Schemes
# These are defined to satisfy the rdfs:range restrictions of various NORIA properties.
# =============================================================================

# KOS Schemes
<https://w3id.org/noria/kos/application/type> a skos:ConceptScheme ; rdfs:label "Application Type Scheme"@en .
